title: Helping Kids Discover Their Identity in Christ
itunes:author: Guests: Ray Vander Laan
itunes:summary: The world tells your kids they must conform in order to fit in. John and Danny discuss believers' true identity as seen in scripture. Featuring Ray Vander Laan. Find us online at focusonthefamily.com/parentingpodcast or call 1-800-A-FAMILY.
